The paper discusses security and privacy implications of mixed reality technology, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper also discusses human-computer interaction (cs.HC), computer vision (cs.CV), and cyber-physical systems (cs.CY) which are all relevant to mixed reality. The paper also mentions mobile devices, wearables, and IoT (cs.SI) which are related to the broader context of mixed reality.
